sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Server
    participant Temporal as Temporal Server
    participant Worker as Temporal Worker
    participant LiteLLM
    participant Tools as Tool / MCP Server
    participant Search as Search Tools
    participant MinIO
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis
    participant Email as Email Provider

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client, DB: 1. AgentRunWorkflow -- LLM call with tool use and human approval
        Client->>API: POST /conversations/{id}/messages
        API->>DB: Insert user Message row
        API->>Temporal: startWorkflow("AgentRunWorkflow", input)
        API-->>Client: 202 Accepted (workflowId)

        loop Agent Loop (until no more tool calls)
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute runLLMActivity
            Worker->>LiteLLM: chat.completions.create (streaming)
            LiteLLM-->>Worker: Token stream + tool_calls[]
            Worker->>DB: Upsert assistant Message (streamed tokens)
            Worker-->>Temporal: Return tool_calls[] or final response

            alt Tool calls present
                alt Tool requires human approval
                    Temporal->>API: Signal: approval_requested
                    API-->>Client: SSE event: approval_requested
                    Client->>API: POST /workflows/{id}/approve
                    API->>Temporal: Signal: approval_granted
                end

                Temporal->>Worker: Execute toolCallActivity
                Worker->>Tools: Invoke tool / MCP server
                Tools-->>Worker: Tool result
                Worker->>DB: Insert tool result Message
                Worker-->>Temporal: Tool results (feed back to LLM)
            end
        end

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute finalizeActivity
        Worker->>DB: Update Message status = completed
        Worker->>API: Signal: workflow_complete
        API-->>Client: SSE event: stream.done
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client, DB: 2. DeepResearchWorkflow -- Parallel search, synthesis, citations
        Client->>API: POST /research (query, depth)
        API->>Temporal: startWorkflow("DeepResearchWorkflow", query)
        API-->>Client: 202 Accepted (workflowId)

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute planSearchActivity
        Worker->>LiteLLM: Generate search sub-queries
        LiteLLM-->>Worker: sub-queries[]
        Worker-->>Temporal: SearchPlan

        par Parallel Search Execution
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute searchActivity(query_1)
            Worker->>Search: Web search / knowledge base
            Search-->>Worker: Results batch 1
        and
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute searchActivity(query_2)
            Worker->>Search: Web search / knowledge base
            Search-->>Worker: Results batch 2
        and
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute searchActivity(query_N)
            Worker->>Search: Web search / knowledge base
            Search-->>Worker: Results batch N
        end

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute synthesisActivity
        Worker->>LiteLLM: Synthesize all results into report
        LiteLLM-->>Worker: Draft report with inline refs
        Worker-->>Temporal: DraftReport

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute citationActivity
        Worker->>LiteLLM: Extract and format citations
        LiteLLM-->>Worker: Verified citations[]
        Worker-->>Temporal: CitedReport

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute finalizeReportActivity
        Worker->>DB: Store report + citations + sources
        Worker-->>Temporal: Complete

        API-->>Client: SSE event: research.done (reportId)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client, DB: 3. FileIngestionWorkflow -- Extract, chunk, embed, upsert
        Client->>API: POST /knowledge/{collectionId}/documents (file)
        API->>MinIO: Upload raw file
        API->>DB: Insert Document row (status: processing)
        API->>Temporal: startWorkflow("FileIngestionWorkflow", docId)
        API-->>Client: 202 Accepted (documentId)

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute extractTextActivity
        Worker->>MinIO: Download raw file
        Worker->>Worker: Parse PDF / DOCX / MD / TXT / HTML
        Worker-->>Temporal: ExtractedText

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute chunkActivity
        Worker->>Worker: Split into chunks (token-aware, overlap)
        Worker-->>Temporal: Chunk[]

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute embedActivity
        Worker->>LiteLLM: POST /embeddings (batch)
        LiteLLM-->>Worker: vector[]
        Worker-->>Temporal: EmbeddedChunk[]

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute upsertActivity
        Worker->>DB: Bulk INSERT chunks + vectors (pgvector)
        Worker->>DB: Update Document status = ready
        Worker-->>Temporal: Complete

        API-->>Client: SSE event: document.ready
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Client, DB: 4. KnowledgeReindexWorkflow -- Re-embed all documents in collection
        Client->>API: POST /knowledge/{collectionId}/reindex
        API->>Temporal: startWorkflow("KnowledgeReindexWorkflow", collectionId)
        API-->>Client: 202 Accepted (workflowId)

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute listDocumentsActivity
        Worker->>DB: SELECT documents WHERE collection_id = X
        Worker-->>Temporal: documentIds[]

        loop For each document (batched)
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute reindexDocumentActivity(docId)
            Worker->>DB: Load existing chunks for document
            Worker->>LiteLLM: POST /embeddings (re-embed chunks)
            LiteLLM-->>Worker: New vectors
            Worker->>DB: UPDATE chunk vectors (pgvector)
            Worker-->>Temporal: Progress update
        end

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute rebuildIndexActivity
        Worker->>DB: REINDEX HNSW index on collection partition
        Worker->>DB: Update collection metadata (last_reindexed_at)
        Worker-->>Temporal: Complete

        API-->>Client: SSE event: reindex.complete
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over Client, Email: 5. ScheduledAgentWorkflow -- Cron-triggered agent run
        Note right of Temporal: Triggered by Temporal cron schedule
        Temporal->>Worker: Execute loadScheduleActivity
        Worker->>DB: Load agent config + schedule context
        Worker-->>Temporal: AgentConfig + last run context

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute runScheduledAgentActivity
        Worker->>LiteLLM: chat.completions.create (with system prompt)
        LiteLLM-->>Worker: Agent response
        Worker-->>Temporal: AgentResult

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute persistResultActivity
        Worker->>DB: Insert Conversation + Messages
        Worker->>DB: Update schedule (last_run_at, next_run_at)
        Worker-->>Temporal: Stored

        alt Agent produced actionable output
            Temporal->>Temporal: Start child NotificationWorkflow
        end
    end

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client, Email: 6. NotificationWorkflow -- Multi-channel notification delivery
        Note right of Temporal: Started by parent workflow or API

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute resolveRecipientsActivity
        Worker->>DB: Load user preferences + notification settings
        Worker-->>Temporal: Recipients with preferred channels

        par Parallel channel delivery
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute inAppNotifyActivity
            Worker->>DB: INSERT notification row
            Worker->>Redis: PUBLISH notification channel
            Note right of Redis: SSE push to connected clients
        and
            Temporal->>Worker: Execute emailNotifyActivity
            Worker->>Email: Send transactional email
            Email-->>Worker: Delivery status
            Worker->>DB: Update notification (email_sent_at)
        end

        Temporal->>Worker: Execute markDeliveredActivity
        Worker->>DB: Update notification status = delivered
        Worker-->>Temporal: Complete
    end
